ome enormous defect, something vital is wanting in us, nor is it difficult =
to lay our finger on the spot. We have all things else, but we are empty of=
 strength, void of energy. We have abandoned Shakti and are therefore aband=
oned by Shakti. The Mother is not in our hearts, in our brains, in our arms=
.
> 
